<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Lalilies Community</title>

<style>
body{
background:#000;
color:white;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
padding:20px;
}

h1{
color:#ffd700;
text-align:center;
}

.post{
background:#111;
border:1px solid #ffd700;
border-radius:12px;
padding:15px;
margin:20px 0;
}

.username{
color:#ffd700;
font-weight:bold;
}

button{
background:#ffd700;
color:black;
border:none;
padding:10px 18px;
border-radius:8px;
font-weight:bold;
margin-top:20px;
}

textarea{
width:100%;
height:100px;
background:#111;
color:white;
border:1px solid #ffd700;
border-radius:8px;
padding:10px;
}

input{
width:100%;
padding:10px;
margin-bottom:10px;
background:#111;
color:white;
border:1px solid #ffd700;
border-radius:8px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>💬 Lalilies Fan Community</h1>

<div class="post">
<div class="username">LisaFan001</div>
<p>Let's stream Lisa's latest songs today! 🎵🔥</p>
</div>

<div class="post">
<div class="username">BlackpinkForever</div>
<p>What's your favorite Lisa performance so far? 👑</p>
</div>

<div class="post">
<div class="username">LalisaSupport</div>
<p>Goal: 10 million streams this week! 🚀</p>
</div>

<h2 style="color:#ffd700;">Create a Post</h2>

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Username">

<textarea placeholder="Write your message here..."></textarea>

<br>

<button>Post Message</button>

<br><br>

<a href="index.html">
<button>← Back to Home</button>
</a>

</body>
</html>
